n"></div></div></div><div class="uppercase-text is-bold">Warm welcome every time</div><div><div data-wf--dot--variant="base" class="dot"><div class="dot-animation"></div></div></div></div><h2 class="heading is-regular">Where elegance meets ease</h2><p class="paragraph-small">Natural materials, soft light, and timelesstextures shape every corner of the hotel. Locally crafted interiors and arm, balanced color palette.</p><a data-wf--main-button--variant="base" href="/location" class="button w-inline-block"><div class="button-text">Location</div><div class="button-bg"></div><div class="button-icon-block"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68d6a56b32400004b53bc0e9/68e5494733197fb0b4bf700d_arrow-icon-11.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="button-icon"/></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-absolute-gradient"></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="sticky-title-size is-light"><div class="sticky-title-layout is-marquee"><div data-wf--marquee-titles--variant="dark" class="marquee-titles"><div class="marquee-wrapper"><div class="marquee-title">Wellness</div><div class="marquee-dash"></div><div class="marquee-title">Relax</div><div class="marquee-dash"></div><div class="marquee-title">Wellness</div><div class="marquee-dash"></div><div class="marquee-title">Relax</div><div class="marquee-dash"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bg-relative-gradient-darker"></div><div class="in-nutshell"><div class="in-nutshell-sticky"><div class="in-nutshell-title"><div class="text-with-dots"><div class="uppercase-text is-bold">relax</div><div><div data-wf--dot--variant="base" class="dot"><div class="dot-animation"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="in-nutshell-wrapper"><div class="in-nutshell-block"><h3 class="heading is-regular">Treatments</h3><div class="in-nutshell-p is-1st"><p class="paragraph-small">Unwind with therapies inspired by both traditional techniques. From full-body massages to targeted treatments.</p></div><div class="in-nuts